IS  - 3
PB  - Academy of Management
N2  - The relation of age to pay rates for 197 Hispanic, black, and white non-managerial workers of both sexes was examined in two organizations. Disparity between the pay rates of women and minority group members, relative to white men, increased with age when organizational tenure, education, and skills were controlled.
